Lets just load the training data and have at it.

Inspection of the data indicated there was some room for cleaning and selecting a subset of parameters. We build a working set.

##    A    B    C    D    E 
## 5580 3797 3422 3216 3607

EDA and Feature Selection

Now the data has be trimmed and filtered down to a working set we can seperate out a testing set for cross validation.

Modelling

Although we tried various methods to split correct and flawed exercises, we will run all categories through the random forest algorithm rather than the two stage seperation.
